cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes attention mechanisms to improve the performance and interpretability of recurrent neural networks for human activity recognition. This work involves machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.HC, cs.AI, and cs.NE.
